    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike Deckbuilder</h2><br>Repeatedly acquire and delete cards to strengthen your deck power and fight back against enemy automata.<br>Over 300 different cards, each with its own unique effect, can be combined to create endless strategies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Card Categories</h2><br>This title features four different card categories.<br><br><strong>Active Card</strong><br>It is a basic card whose effect is applied immediately upon use.<br><br><strong>Permanent Card</strong><br>It has the effect of static.<br><br><strong>Counter Card</strong><br>It can be activated at any time, including the opponent's turn. It has a special effect that allows you to interfere with your opponent's actions.<br><br><strong>Artifact Card</strong><br>It is a powerful card that is always effective if you have it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character</h2><br>You can start the game by choosing one of two characters, &quot;Lydia&quot; and &quot;Smyrna&quot;.<br>Each character has its own features and different cards that can be acquired, allowing you to play with a completely different strategy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>An artifact with a power that cannot be explained by current technology.<br>To retrieve the artifact, Lydia and Smyrna enter a dungeon to discover the secrets of the dungeon...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Streaming, Video Creation</h2><br>As long as the following conditions are met, you are free to create streaming and play videos, regardless of whether you are an individual or a company, and whether or not you monetization your work.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The URL to the Steam store page must be included.</li></ul>",
